  <title>Grizzly 1.9.x</title>

  <para>The Grizzly 1.9.x documentation</para>
    <section>
        <title>System Requirements</title>
        
        <para>The system requirements for Grizzly 1.9.x are quite simple. Basically,
            Grizzly is able to run on any platform that <link xlink:href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/index.html">JDK
                1.5</link> is available on.</para>
    </section>
